overview: A bride has disappeared from a suite at a five-star hotel, whose wedding to one of the country's most eligible suitors is to take place the next day. Broken phone, torn photo, scattered things in the room - pre-wedding jitters or kidnapping? In the course of the investigation, the operatives reveal many secrets of the guests who were on the same floor that night with the disappeared. Everything becomes completely confusing when a mysterious message comes to the girl's phone, which was discovered by the police - "I am here."
title: I'm Here
